trans-unit.source: Creates the theme-specific look for [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_avalonwinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-avalonwinfx-md.md)] <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Button"></xref> elements.
trans-unit.target: Cria o aspeto de tema específicos para [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_avalonwinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-avalonwinfx-md.md)] <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Button"> </xref> elementos.

trans-unit.source: The actual appearance of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button> is dependent on which theme is active on the user's system.
trans-unit.target: O aspeto real do <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>depende de qual tema está ativo no sistema do utilizador.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>

trans-unit.source: The properties of this class allow [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_avalonwinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-avalonwinfx-md.md)] to set the appearance based on the current theme.
trans-unit.target: As propriedades desta classe permitem [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_avalonwinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-avalonwinfx-md.md)] para definir o aspecto com base no tema actual.

trans-unit.source: In XAML usage, a ButtonChrome object element can also have child content, which can be a single <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> that sets the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Decorator.Child%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Na utilização XAML, um elemento de objecto ButtonChrome também pode ter conteúdo subordinado, o que pode ser um único <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>que define o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Decorator.Child%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Decorator.Child%2A> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement>

trans-unit.target: Normalmente, os prefixos xmlns e mapeamentos são definidos num elemento raiz XAML (não apresentado).
